@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About us";
}
<style>
    body {
        background-color: #18332f;
        color: white;
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }

    .home-container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        height: 100vh;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
    }
    .bubble-text {
        font-size: 48px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #ffffff;
        background-color: #1a4a43;
        border-radius: 40px;
        padding: 20px 40px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        display: inline-block;
    }
    .subtext {
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 500;
        margin-top: 10px;
        color: #ffffff;
    }

    .button {
        background-color: #4caf50;
        color: white;
        padding: 12px 28px;
        font-size: 20px;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        cursor: pointer;
        margin-top: 30px;
        transition: background-color 0.3s;
        display: inline-block;
    }

    .button:hover {
        background-color: #388e3c;
    }
</style>

<div class="home-container">
    <h1 class="bubble-text">Rooted in Tech, Growing with NATURE</h1>
    <p class="subtext">At Agri-Energy Connect, we believe in a future where agriculture and sustainable energy work hand in hand. Our platform serves as a dynamic bridge between farmers and energy providers, empowering agricultural communities with innovative tools and resources to thrive in an eco-conscious world.

Founded with the vision of transforming how farmers access, manage, and benefit from clean energy solutions, we offer a seamless, user-friendly interface where farmers can showcase their products, connect with reliable partners, and tap into renewable energy opportunities.

By integrating technology with agriculture, we’re not just supporting today’s growers — we’re nurturing a more resilient and sustainable tomorrow. <br>

Agri-Energy Connect: Powering Agriculture, Sustaining Tomorrow.</p>

<button class="button" onclick="location.href='@Url.Action("Index", "Home")'">Home</button>
